reviews.review_text:
Well Done! Nice job on this matrix!  Really gives the feeling of being there, good show to boot!

If you haven't checked this one out yet, do yourself a favor, I'm sure you'll be pleased.

Like a child, she is pure, she is not to blame Love the sound on this Matrix..I also love the song selection from start to finish! The Ramble on Rose stood out along with Looks Like Rain> Mighty Swell to end the 1st set..A very nice Help>Slip>Franklins to open a sweet 2nd set and I also like the like the Truckin'>Black Peter>Not Fade out of space!! Revolution encore cause you know we all want to change the world! so please..GIVE IT A WHIRL!! Forever Grateful>Forever Dead!!! NYC BABY!!
